Robin Curtis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Curtis 0 Robin Curtis (born June 15, 1956) is an American real estate broker and actress. She is best known for replacing Kirstie Alley in the role of Vulcan Lieutenant Saavik in the films Star Trek III: The Search for Spock and Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home.
